### Student Registration - Step 1: Send OTP
POST http://localhost:3000/api/student/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "fullName": "Test Student",
  "email": "your-test-email@gmail.com",
  "enrollmentNumber": "CS2024999",
  "branch": "Computer Science",
  "year": "3",
  "deviceId": "test_device_12345"
}

### Student Registration - Step 2: Verify OTP
POST http://localhost:3000/api/student/verify-registration
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "your-test-email@gmail.com",
  "otp": "123456"
}

